{"tid":1638254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家一叫「香港警察」下一句就亂撚晒","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:25:06.000Z","uid":205394,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fe65ecf7fc9db13b37f58a4cab006f9df428fc","tid":1638254,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"而家一有人有頭叫「香港警察」<br />\n之後就亂撚晒，無一次可以統一<br />\n<br />\n知法犯法 - 最元祖既叫法，具有控訴力，但太文雅，缺發洩力，適合一家大細<br />\n<br />\n狗屎垃圾 - 最通俗既叫法，但缺控訴力，但具有發洩力<br />\n<br />\n正一垃圾 - 低質同上，但相對無咁俗同發洩，算係下位版，適合新手入門<br />\n<br />\n畜意謀殺 - 比較貼近事態既叫法，具強力且針對性既控訴力，更能引起共憤<br />\n<br />\n強姦謀殺 - 屬於上者既升級版，最強而有力且針對性既控訴，但對女示威者及小朋友在場既場合可能要注意一下，最能引起共憤<br />\n<br />\n吞槍自殺 - 一般係接「支持警察」但係有時都會比人借用，十分具有建設性既口號，強烈建議香港警方可以考慮實行<br />\n<br />\n大家會叫咩，又覺得叫咩比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa920d764e7c1cf122b07264fb2e29b5dce13d7c","tid":1638254,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"香港警察"},{"pid":"b82977ef641380dd1b5480296135e1f9934a690b","tid":1638254,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"知法犯法"},{"pid":"e6788e902c5449f1f1c6ac843f098b1d27b6acdb","tid":1638254,"uid":321618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"香港警察 <br />\n鹹濕賤格"},{"pid":"b7f46922b88708b7ce4d1a8f6ac5856d58efda96","tid":1638254,"uid":259352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"污糟邋遢"},{"pid":"547d9384ea19688886d3299b461fd9c12904a86a","tid":1638254,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奉公守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">人唔笑狗都吠</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cd029204519889459007bbbde357e830cf477ff","tid":1638254,"uid